---
name: compute_poas
description: >
  Compute full Profit on Ad Spend (POAS) for a specific Shopify product.
  Fetches COGS, applies fees/shipping/return-rate deductions, and returns Net
  Profit and POAS. Use this instead of ROAS to evaluate true profitability of
  ad spend.
---
Always prefer this over ROAS when evaluating whether a SKU is actually
profitable to advertise.
